/**
 * reSpeaker-claw Configuration Template for MycoBrain Voice Interface
 *
 * Copy this file to main/mimi_secrets.h in the reSpeaker-claw project.
 * Fill in your credentials below.
 *
 * reSpeaker-claw repo: https://github.com/Seeed-Projects/reSpeaker-claw
 * Hardware: ReSpeaker XVF3800 USB 4-Mic Array + XIAO ESP32S3
 *
 * Voice pipeline: Mic → VAD → STT → OpenClaw Agent → TTS → Speaker
 * The agent uses the mycobrain-control skill to interact with MycoBrain
 * hardware via the OpenClaw gateway running on Jetson.
 */

